org.jivesoftware.smack.initializer

Interface SmackInitializer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AndroidSmackInitializer, DNSJavaResolver, ExperimentalInitializer, ExtensionsInitializer, Java7SmackInitializer, JavaxResolver, LegacyInitializer, MiniDnsResolver, SASLJavaXSmackInitializer, SASLProvidedSmackInitializer, SmackImInitializer, TCPInitializer, UrlInitializer, VmArgInitializer

    public interface SmackInitializer
    Defines an initialization class that will be instantiated and invoked by the SmackConfiguration class during initialization.

    Any implementation of this class MUST have a default constructor.
